JIRA should have an option to verify that a user owns the email address they claim to have, when signing up for an account.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *JIRA Server*. Using *JIRA Cloud*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JRACLOUD-3594].
  {panel}

It would be nice to be able to add a description of an attachment when you attach it (instead of just a general comment).  This description would appear in the Manage Attachments table next to the attachment.

Currently you can enter a general comment but that gets lost in the comment list and is difficult to locate when viewing the list of attachments.

